        "authorId" : "94ae5814-8889-4328-9b58-745772997928",
        "body" : "What would be the gain? In tests I don't really care about duplicate code. I prefer to use the actual values for comparisons. That way it does not depend on the templating engine (like `{{hostvars['h1'].host_var}}` might equal to `{{ host_var }}` but if it is templated to an incorrect value we won't find out because the comparison would still be true, however it's unlikely).",
        "createdAt" : "2019-11-06T07:22:08Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2019-11-06T07:22:08Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "94ae5814-8889-4328-9b58-745772997928",
