        "authorId" : "7243ee41-f7f6-470f-8b39-aec91451b808",
        "body" : "Given it's the actual templating engine that's being tested I guess hard coded values makes sense.  I would have switched to the variable just because folks looking to write their first tests often look for simple examples and assume the simple example is the way it should always be done.",
